        </li>
        <li><strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native, Flutter, Swift, Kotlin</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Databases:</strong> PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis, Elasticsearch
        </li>
        <li><strong>Cloud:</strong> AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, DigitalOcean</li>
        <li>
          <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins, GitLab CI/CD, Terraform
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Our Development Process</h3>
      <p>
        We follow agile methodologies to ensure transparency, flexibility, and
