        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Support & Maintenance:</strong> Ongoing support, updates, and enhancements
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Why Choose Us</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Proven Expertise</h4><p>
            15+ years of experience delivering successful projects across
            various industries and technologies.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Agile Methodology</h4><p>
            Flexible, iterative approach that adapts to changing requirements
